 "text": "Okay, after digging through the pkg source code, I found a possible workaround. Add following line to \"/usr/local/etc/pkg.conf\":\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------\nOSVERSION = 1200056;\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nfor the 12 users.\n\n\nRespective:\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------\nOSVERSION = 1101001\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nfor the 11 users.\n\n\nAfter that, the repository updates should be working again..."
}